<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>sʿyd bạz</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- hā naḥ̊nu yā rabã ạl̊waray̱
 qad̊ jī̊̉nā nab̊tagẖī ạlsũjūd̊
 min̊ ḥaẘli fādīnā ạl̊ḥabīb̊
 nasẖ̊kuruka ʿan̊ kulĩ jūd̊

[V2]
 2- fāi̹nãka fī sẖakẖ̊ṣihi
 ạikẖ̊tar̊tanā mun̊dẖu ạlạảzal̊
 wajāʾa fī mil̊ʾi ạlzãmān̊
 mutamĩmaⁿạ kulã ạl̊ʿamal̊:

[V3]
 3- ʿanãạ qaḍay̱ faẘqa ạlṣãlīb̊
 fāảk̊mala masarãtak̊
 waradã maj̊daka ạlsãlīb̊
 mukamĩlạaⁿ masẖīyảtak̊

[V4]
 4- wāản̊ta ạảyũhā ạl̊ḥanūn̊
 jaʿal̊tahu faẘqa ạl̊jamīʿ̊
 ạảqam̊tahu mukẖalĩṣaⁿạ
 warāʿīaⁿạ ʿalay̱ ạl̊qaṭīʿ̊

[V5]
 5- biạs̊mihi naḥ̊nu nas̊judu
 min̊ qal̊binā nuh̊dī ạltẖãnā
 muradĩdīna mad̊ḥaka
 ạảbānā wāi̹lahanā</lyrics>
<title>hạ nḥn yạ rb ạlwry̱</title>
</song>